http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Vijayawada/SCR-General-Manager-inspects-Renigunta-Guntakal-section/article13978536.ece

SCR General Manager Ravindra Gupta conducted an inspection of Renigunta-Guntakal section on Guntakal Division on Saturday and inaugurated a few facilities at different stations during his inspection.The General Manager commenced his inspection from Renigunta Railway station where he inaugurated a remodeled running room and an online Train Running Status Display System.During a window trailing inspection of the Renigunta-Pullampet section, he stopped at an Un-Manned Level Crossing Gate between Tuliampet and Razampeta stations and carried out a scrutiny of essential safety equipments, approach roads, track visibility, first aid availability and etc.He inaugurated a renovated Crew Booking Lobby at Nandalur railway station.